{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-novel-version-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon; Novel Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-20",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/themaltesefalconnovel_2603_librivox/maltesefalcon_20_hammett_128kb.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "If They Hang You",
  "reader_name": "NLizer",
  "page_num": 4,
  "page_total": 6,
  "page_start_sec": 733.76,
  "page_end_sec": 974.34,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.529,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 733.76,
      "end": 734.82,
      "text": "She said in a small,"
    },
    {
      "start": 734.84,
      "end": 735.52,
      "text": "parched voice,"
    },
    {
      "start": 736.24,
      "end": 736.58,
      "text": "you're not.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 737.15,
      "end": 740.62,
      "text": "she could get no other words out spade's face",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 740.62,
      "end": 743.38,
      "text": "was yellow white now his mouth smiled and there"
    },
    {
      "start": 743.38,
      "end": 744.78,
      "text": "were smile wrinkles around his"
    },
    {
      "start": 744.78,
      "end": 747.78,
      "text": "glittering eyes his voice was soft gentle"
    },
    {
      "start": 748.68,
      "end": 750.46,
      "text": "he said i'm going to",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 750.54,
      "end": 751.18,
      "text": "send you over"
    },
    {
      "start": 751.7,
      "end": 752.1,
      "text": "the chances"
    },
    {
      "start": 752.64,
      "end": 754.0,
      "text": "are you'll get off with life",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 754.62,
      "end": 756.64,
      "text": "that means you'll be out again in 20 years",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 756.88,
      "end": 760.12,
      "text": "you're an angel i'll wait for you he cleared his throat"
    },
    {
      "start": 760.74,
      "end": 763.08,
      "text": "if they hang you i'll always remember you",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 764.0,
      "end": 766.58,
      "text": "she dropped her hands and stood erect her face",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 766.58,
      "end": 768.62,
      "text": "became smooth and untroubled except for the"
    },
    {
      "start": 768.84,
      "end": 771.92,
      "text": "faintest of dubious glints in her eyes she smiled"
    },
    {
      "start": 771.92,
      "end": 775.72,
      "text": "back at him gently don't sam don't say that even"
    },
    {
      "start": 775.72,
      "end": 776.3,
      "text": "in fun"
    },
    {
      "start": 777.1,
      "end": 780.88,
      "text": "oh you frightened me for a moment i really thought you",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 781.52,
      "end": 783.2,
      "text": "you know you do such wild and",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 783.26,
      "end": 784.6,
      "text": "unpredictable things that"
    },
    {
      "start": 785.26,
      "end": 785.96,
      "text": "she broke off",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 786.76,
      "end": 789.38,
      "text": "she thrust her face forward and stared deep into his eyes",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 789.9,
      "end": 791.76,
      "text": "Her cheeks and the flesh around her mouth"
    },
    {
      "start": 791.76,
      "end": 794.22,
      "text": "shivered and fear came back into her eyes."
    },
    {
      "start": 795.08,
      "end": 795.26,
      "text": "What?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 795.5,
      "end": 795.6,
      "text": "Sam!"
    },
    {
      "start": 796.81,
      "end": 799.86,
      "text": "She put her hands to her throat again and lost her erectness.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 800.544,
      "end": 801.06,
      "text": "Spade laughed.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 801.42,
      "end": 802.4,
      "text": "His yellow"
    },
    {
      "start": 802.48,
      "end": 805.08,
      "text": "white face was damp with sweat and though he held"
    },
    {
      "start": 805.08,
      "end": 807.72,
      "text": "his smile he could not hold softness in his voice."
    },
    {
      "start": 808.38,
      "end": 808.86,
      "text": "He croaked,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 809.0,
      "end": 810.28,
      "text": "don't be silly."
    },
    {
      "start": 810.52,
      "end": 812.02,
      "text": "You're taking the fall."
    },
    {
      "start": 812.31,
      "end": 814.92,
      "text": "One of us has got to take it after the"
    },
    {
      "start": 815.06,
      "end": 816.26,
      "text": "Talking those birds will do."
    },
    {
      "start": 816.46,
      "end": 817.48,
      "text": "They'd hang me,"
    },
    {
      "start": 817.56,
      "end": 817.84,
      "text": "sure."
    },
    {
      "start": 818.08,
      "end": 819.96,
      "text": "You're likely to get a better break."
    },
    {
      "start": 820.6,
      "end": 820.72,
      "text": "Well,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 820.96,
      "end": 821.152,
      "text": "but,"
    },
    {
      "start": 822.02,
      "end": 822.92,
      "text": "but Sam,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 823.04,
      "end": 823.74,
      "text": "you can't."
    },
    {
      "start": 823.74,
      "end": 825.78,
      "text": "Not after what we've been to each other."
    },
    {
      "start": 825.84,
      "end": 826.56,
      "text": "You can't."
    },
    {
      "start": 827.264,
      "end": 828.4,
      "text": "Like hell I can't.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 829.32,
      "end": 830.74,
      "text": "She took a long trembling breath.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 831.52,
      "end": 832.62,
      "text": "You've been playing with me?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 832.74,
      "end": 833.29,
      "text": "Only"
    },
    {
      "start": 833.6,
      "end": 835.72,
      "text": "pretending you cared to trap me like this?"
    },
    {
      "start": 836.3,
      "end": 837.66,
      "text": "You didn't care at all?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 838.2,
      "end": 840.94,
      "text": "You didn't don't love me?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 841.49,
      "end": 842.8,
      "text": "I think I do,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 842.96,
      "end": 843.72,
      "text": "Spade said."
    },
    {
      "start": 843.92,
      "end": 844.5,
      "text": "What of it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 845.2,
      "end": 847.94,
      "text": "The muscles holding his smile in place stood out like whales.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 848.8,
      "end": 849.53,
      "text": "I'm not Thursby.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 849.72,
      "end": 850.92,
      "text": "I'm not Jacoby."
    },
    {
      "start": 851.6,
      "end": 853.32,
      "text": "I won't play the sap for you.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 854.02,
      "end": 854.78,
      "text": "That is not just,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 855.02,
      "end": 855.76,
      "text": "she cried."
    },
    {
      "start": 856.768,
      "end": 857.82,
      "text": "Tears came to her eyes.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 857.98,
      "end": 858.78,
      "text": "It's unfair."
    },
    {
      "start": 859.2,
      "end": 860.88,
      "text": "It's contemptible of you."
    },
    {
      "start": 861.0,
      "end": 862.44,
      "text": "You know it was not that."
    },
    {
      "start": 862.62,
      "end": 863.68,
      "text": "You can't say that."
    },
    {
      "start": 864.62,
      "end": 865.52,
      "text": "Like hell I can't,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 865.56,
      "end": 866.24,
      "text": "Spade said."
    },
    {
      "start": 866.46,
      "end": 869.2,
      "text": "You came into my bed to stop me asking questions."
    },
    {
      "start": 870.08,
      "end": 873.68,
      "text": "You led me out yesterday for Gutman with that phony call for help.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 874.4,
      "end": 876.14,
      "text": "Last night you came here with them and",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 876.14,
      "end": 878.52,
      "text": "waited outside for me and came in with me."
    },
    {
      "start": 879.42,
      "end": 881.7,
      "text": "You were in my arms when the trap was sprung.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 882.28,
      "end": 885.8,
      "text": "I couldn't have gone for a gun if I'd had one on me and",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 885.8,
      "end": 888.62,
      "text": "couldn't have made a fight of it if I had wanted to."
    },
    {
      "start": 889.34,
      "end": 891.1,
      "text": "And if they didn't take you away with them,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 891.36,
      "end": 893.88,
      "text": "it was only because Gutman's got too much sense to"
    },
    {
      "start": 893.88,
      "end": 896.76,
      "text": "trust you except for short stretches when he has to."
    },
    {
      "start": 897.1,
      "end": 899.84,
      "text": "and because he thought I'd play the sap for you and,"
    },
    {
      "start": 900.84,
      "end": 901.98,
      "text": "not wanting to hurt you,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 902.14,
      "end": 903.18,
      "text": "wouldn't be able"
    },
    {
      "start": 903.18,
      "end": 903.86,
      "text": "to hurt him?"
    },
    {
      "start": 905.152,
      "end": 907.04,
      "text": "Bridget O'Shaughnessy blinked her tears away.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 907.8,
      "end": 909.48,
      "text": "She took a step towards him and stood",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 909.58,
      "end": 910.64,
      "text": "looking him in the eyes,"
    },
    {
      "start": 910.68,
      "end": 911.4,
      "text": "straight and proud."
    },
    {
      "start": 911.78,
      "end": 913.24,
      "text": "You called me a liar,"
    },
    {
      "start": 913.42,
      "end": 914.0,
      "text": "she said."
    },
    {
      "start": 914.2,
      "end": 915.56,
      "text": "Now you are lying."
    },
    {
      "start": 916.36,
      "end": 918.86,
      "text": "You're lying if you say you don't know down in",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 918.86,
      "end": 921.24,
      "text": "your heart that in spite of anything I've done,"
    },
    {
      "start": 921.44,
      "end": 922.12,
      "text": "I love you."
    },
    {
      "start": 923.104,
      "end": 923.94,
      "text": "Spade made a short,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 924.02,
      "end": 924.62,
      "text": "abrupt bow."
    },
    {
      "start": 924.92,
      "end": 927.2,
      "text": "His eyes were becoming bloodshot,"
    },
    {
      "start": 927.68,
      "end": 928.2,
      "text": "but there was no"
    },
    {
      "start": 928.2,
      "end": 930.14,
      "text": "other change in his damp and yellowish,"
    },
    {
      "start": 930.18,
      "end": 931.76,
      "text": "fixedly smiling face."
    },
    {
      "start": 932.86,
      "end": 933.3,
      "text": "Maybe I do,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 933.42,
      "end": 933.76,
      "text": "he said."
    },
    {
      "start": 933.94,
      "end": 934.56,
      "text": "What of it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 934.94,
      "end": 935.84,
      "text": "I should trust you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 936.8,
      "end": 940.16,
      "text": "You who arranged that nice little trick for my predecessor,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 940.4,
      "end": 940.88,
      "text": "Thursby?"
    },
    {
      "start": 941.06,
      "end": 941.76,
      "text": "You"
    },
    {
      "start": 942.0,
      "end": 942.9,
      "text": "who knocked off Miles,"
    },
    {
      "start": 943.14,
      "end": 944.7,
      "text": "a man you had nothing against,"
    },
    {
      "start": 944.88,
      "end": 945.9,
      "text": "in cold blood,"
    },
    {
      "start": 946.14,
      "end": 947.54,
      "text": "just like swatting a fly"
    },
    {
      "start": 947.82,
      "end": 949.52,
      "text": "for the sake of double-crossing Thursby?"
    },
    {
      "start": 950.42,
      "end": 951.8,
      "text": "You who double-crossed Gutman,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 952.0,
      "end": 952.48,
      "text": "Cairo,"
    },
    {
      "start": 952.68,
      "end": 953.24,
      "text": "Thursby,"
    },
    {
      "start": 953.36,
      "end": 953.76,
      "text": "one,"
    },
    {
      "start": 953.9,
      "end": 954.06,
      "text": "two,"
    },
    {
      "start": 954.12,
      "end": 954.3,
      "text": "three?"
    },
    {
      "start": 954.78,
      "end": 957.64,
      "text": "You who've never played square with me for"
    },
    {
      "start": 957.64,
      "end": 960.58,
      "text": "half an hour at a stretch since I've known you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 961.14,
      "end": 962.06,
      "text": "I should trust you?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 962.32,
      "end": 962.42,
      "text": "No,"
    },
    {
      "start": 963.08,
      "end": 963.38,
      "text": "no,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 963.4,
      "end": 963.8,
      "text": "darling."
    },
    {
      "start": 964.32,
      "end": 965.84,
      "text": "I wouldn't do it even if I could."
    },
    {
      "start": 966.04,
      "end": 967.12,
      "text": "Why should I?"
    },
    {
      "start": 968.1,
      "end": 968.7,
      "text": "Her eyes were",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 968.76,
      "end": 969.72,
      "text": "steady under his,"
    },
    {
      "start": 969.96,
      "end": 972.72,
      "text": "and her hushed voice was steady when she replied."
    },
    {
      "start": 973.7,
      "end": 974.34,
      "text": "Why should you?",
      "para_break": true
    }
  ]
}